    <h4>Waffle.io Demo</h4>
    <p>Waffle.io lets teams manage projects using GitHub Issues and Pull Requests. Waffle listens to the actions in your workflow to know when work is started, ready for review, or finished and updates your status automatically. This demo will introduce teams to this powerful, free, and open solution for managing workflow.</p>

